HOW TO USE libtexu ON Sun Solaris 8 (5.8)
-----------------------------------------
1 Copy folder ./terminfo into the home directory and rename its from terminfo to .terminfo
    e.g. $> cp -R from/to/path/terminfo ~/.terminfo
2 Use TERM=xterm-sun
    e.g. $> TERM=xterm-sun; export TERM

NB. xterm-sun copy from Linux 7